GIMP. Any image editing program really, it's a simple effect. Basically the equivalent of manually adding a shadow to something.
>select thing you want to outline, can select transparent background and invert
>make new layer
>fill selection with color
>move layer down
>move layer away
Boom, you got the basic shadow effect.
